{"product_id":"pork-spare-ribs","title":"Pork Spare Ribs","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eJuicy pork spare back ribs prepared in our signature style, par-cooked with our classic dry rub, and marinated in our Sweet BBQ sauce. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIf you're looking for a showstopper for your grill, you've found it.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch3\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eWhat You Get:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/h3\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e2 x Racks of Ribs (Approx. 1kg)\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch3\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eHow to cook\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/h3\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eGrill\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eCook these ribs over a hot fire to crisp up the sauces, place meat side up to start and baste and turn regularly \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eOven \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eTotal cook time - 20 minutes\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003ePreheat oven to 200(C), place ribs in a suitable oven dish and baste with our BBQ sauce generously. After 10 minutes, remove and baste again, and cook for another 10 minutes.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"1kg (Approx.)","offers":[{"title":"Signature Dry Rub","offer_id":42980058988773,"sku":"","price":12.95,"currency_code":"GBP","in_stock":false},{"title":"Sticky BBQ","offer_id":42970502922469,"sku":null,"price":12.95,"currency_code":"GBP","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0645\/6197\/1429\/products\/Spareribs1.jpg?v=1653675761","url":"https:\/\/meatshed.co.uk\/products\/pork-spare-ribs","provider":"Meat Shed","version":"1.0","type":"link"}